#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.5:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Sekhabalavagga"
msgstr "1. Powers of a Trainee"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: sikkhāpaccakkhānasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Sikkhāsutta"
msgstr "5. Disrobing"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: diṭṭheva → diṭṭhe ceva (bj) | dittheva (pts1)
#. VAR: vādānupātā → vādānuvādā (pts1)
msgctxt "an5.5:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vā bhikkhunī vā sikkhaṃ paccakkhāya "
"hīnāyāvattati, tassa diṭṭheva dhamme pañca sahadhammikā vādānupātā gārayhā "
"ṭhānā āgacchanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, any monk or nun who rejects the training and returns to a "
"lesser life deserves rebuke and criticism on five legitimate grounds in the "
"present life."

msgctxt "an5.5:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.5:1.3"
msgid ""
"Saddhāpi nāma te nāhosi kusalesu dhammesu, hirīpi nāma te nāhosi kusalesu "
"dhammesu, ottappampi nāma te nāhosi kusalesu dhammesu, vīriyampi nāma te "
"nāhosi kusalesu dhammesu, paññāpi nāma te nāhosi kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"‘You had no faith, conscience, prudence, energy, or wisdom regarding "
"skillful qualities.’"

msgctxt "an5.5:1.4"
msgid ""
"Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vā bhikkhunī vā sikkhaṃ paccakkhāya "
"hīnāyāvattati, tassa diṭṭheva dhamme ime pañca sahadhammikā vādānupātā "
"gārayhā ṭhānā āgacchanti."
msgstr ""
"Any monk or nun who rejects the training and returns to a lesser life "
"deserves rebuke and criticism on these five legitimate grounds in the "
"present life."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli3.5"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: assumukho → assumukhopi (s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: pāsaṃsā ṭhānā → pāsaṃsaṃ ṭhānaṃ (s1-3)
msgctxt "an5.5:2.1"
msgid ""
"Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vā bhikkhunī vā sahāpi dukkhena sahāpi "
"domanassena assumukho rudamāno paripuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carati, "
"tassa diṭṭheva dhamme pañca sahadhammikā pāsaṃsā ṭhānā āgacchanti."
msgstr ""
"Any monk or nun who lives the full and pure spiritual life in pain and "
"sadness, weeping, with tearful face, deserves praise on five legitimate "
"grounds in the present life."

msgctxt "an5.5:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.5:2.3"
msgid ""
"Saddhāpi nāma te ahosi kusalesu dhammesu, hirīpi nāma te ahosi kusalesu "
"dhammesu, ottappampi nāma te ahosi kusalesu dhammesu, vīriyampi nāma te "
"ahosi kusalesu dhammesu, paññāpi nāma te ahosi kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"‘You had faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and wisdom regarding skillful "
"qualities.’"

msgctxt "an5.5:2.4"
msgid ""
"Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vā bhikkhunī vā sahāpi dukkhena sahāpi "
"domanassena assumukho rudamāno paripuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carati, "
"tassa diṭṭheva dhamme ime pañca sahadhammikā pāsaṃsā ṭhānā āgacchantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Any monk or nun who lives the full and pure spiritual life in pain and "
"sadness, weeping, with tearful face, deserves praise on these five "
"legitimate grounds in the present life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.5:2.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
